girl_dialog: You have the time visit me? Is that a coincidence? Or have you finally learned to read my face?
Do you know what it means to kneel at my feet? Not everyone can endure a Queen’s gaze.
switch_1: I don’t care about my status.
switch_2: I’ll make the Gods recognize our relationship!
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You’re an interesting one… I hope you can handle the pride I rarely show others...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Heh… If you truly have such resolve, I might one day grant you glory—second only to me.

girl_dialog: I put on this wedding dress remind to remind myself… love will always be held in my hands.
switch_1: Guess what will be in my hands in a few seconds?
switch_2: I’ll cherish this bond with you…
girl_dialog_after_switch1: ... I can’t tell if you’re bold or foolish. Few dare to jest with me like this… Humph.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: ... Then hold on tight. If you let go first, I will not forgive you.

girl_dialog: Do you know... for so many years, I’ve been treated as a symbol of authority in Olympus—never as a maiden who can stir someone's heart…
switch_2: I want you to be my one and only mistress.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: You have a sweeter tongue than those around me. But perhaps I’m not used to such tenderness yet...
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Is this a vow to a Goddess… Or a promise to a maiden? Either way, don’t disappoint me.

girl_dialog: Hmm? My posture looks lazy, you say? But lady Loki told me...you would like this pose with a maid outfit...
...Although I'm a shrine maiden of Japan, I never imagined meeting you like this...
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Captivating…? Such words make it harder for me to face you…
girl_dialog_after_switch2: It’s just an outfit, right? I haven’t accepted this role… because I don’t want to be frivolous before you.

girl_dialog: If I fail in my duties, you may correct me… But isn't this way a bit too unusual?
switch_2: But you don’t dislike it, do you?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: ...I’d refuse anyone else… But for you… I’ll try not to make a spectacle of myself.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Please don’t assume my feelings… Even if I'm not resisting, it doesn’t mean I… like it.

girl_dialog: I know it's part of my duty to be looked at… But aren't you staring… too intently?
switch_2: You’re just a feast to the eye.
girl_dialog_after_switch1: No! It’s just… overwhelming. I don’t know how to face it.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: ...If there's something wrong with the outfit, I’ll make it right. But if it’s because of something else… please restrain yourself…

girl_dialog: Oh? You're finally paying me a visit? I almost thought you were avoiding me.
Mmm~ How much longer do I have to wait, dear? Or is this sweet, juicy cake not tempting enough?
switch_1: I just want to admire you a while longer!
switch_2: Why don't you guess what I’m thinking?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Is that so? Then you'll have to hurry...cause a dessert left unattended might be snatched by someone else.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Playing riddles with the Goddess of Mischief? Heh… Your eyes already gave away the answer.

girl_dialog: I can feel the warmth of your breath whenever you approach, darling...tell me, are you my prey tonight?
switch_2: Is this one of those sweet traps?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Hmm... a straight answer like that makes me hesitate. You want to save the best for last, after all.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Trap? Maybe... but isn't it a blessing to fall into my trap?

girl_dialog: Darling, your hands are getting more bolder. Are you looking for some... punishment?
girl_dialog_after_switch1: Oh, my, I didn't expect you to be so forward. Looks like I'll reconsider the severity of this punishment.
girl_dialog_after_switch2: Hurt? That depends on how well you behave... Rest assured, I'm very good at making the punishment tempting...
